OL,7,FThe damning report warned that without
OL,8,Fa radical overhaul of policing
OL,9,Fpractices and culture, there is
OL,10,F'nothing to stop another Couzens
OL,11,Foperating in plain sight'. ITV News'
OL,12,FUK Editor Paul Brand reports
OL,14,FPolice services require a "radical
OL,15,Foverhaul" to its recruitment process
OL,16,Fto stop another operating in "plain
OL,17,Fsight," the first report from the
OL,18,Findependent Angiolini inquiry finds.
