OL,3,CPolice 'overhaul' needed to stop
OL,4,Canother Wayne Couzens hiding in 'plain
OL,5,Csight'
OL,7,FLed by Dame Elish Angiolini, the
OL,8,Finquiry looked into how Couzens, a
OL,9,Fformer armed Metropolitan Police
OL,10,Fofficer, was able to abduct, rape and
OL,11,Fmurder Sarah Everard in March 2021.
OL,13,FTaking into account evidence spanning
OL,14,Fa 20-year-period, it found Couzens
OL,15,F"should never have been a police
OL,16,Fofficer" and opportunities to stop him
OL,17,Fcontinuing his career and offending
OL,18,Fwere continuously missed.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/13
