OL,4,Canother Wayne Couzens hiding in 'plain
OL,5,Csight'
OL,7,FIt demands a "radical overhaul" of
OL,8,Fpolice vetting and recruitment to stop
OL,9,Ffuture offenders like Couzens being
OL,10,Fdenied opportunities to abuse police
OL,11,Fpowers for sexual purpose.
OL,13,FThe report stated three police forces
OL,14,F- Kent Police, Civil Nuclear
OL,15,FConstabulary and the Metropolitan
OL,16,FPolice Service - "allowed him the
OL,17,Fprivilege" of being a police officer
OL,18,Fwhen they should have stopped him and
OL,19,Frepeatedly ignored red flags to stop
OL,20,Fhim continuing his career and
OL,21,Foffending.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/13
