OL,7,FIt also found evidence that Couzens
OL,8,Fallegedly committed a very serious
OL,9,Fsexual assault against a child,
OL,10,Fdescribed as barely in her teens,
OL,11,Fbefore his policing career even
OL,12,Fstarted.
OL,14,FThe report added there were four other
OL,15,Falleged incidents of sexual offending
OL,16,Fthat were not reported to the police,
OL,17,Fand the inquiry believes there may be
OL,18,Fmore victims.
