OL,7,FWhile the inquiry did not make a
OL,8,Fconclusive finding that Ms Everard's
OL,9,Fmurder could have been prevented, it
OL,10,Ffound that Couzens could have been
OL,11,Fsacked if investigations into indecent
OL,12,Fexposure reports had been more
OL,13,Fthorough.
OL,15,FHis crimes were "the culmination of a
OL,16,Ftrajectory of sexually motivated
OL,17,Fbehaviour and offending", including
OL,18,Findecent exposure, the sexual assault
OL,19,Fon a child, sexual touching and
OL,20,Fsharing unsolicited photos of his
OL,21,Fgenitals, the report found.
