OL,7,FIt said there were also allegations he
OL,8,Fpossessed indecent images of children.
OL,10,FThe report found Couzens' history of
OL,11,Falleged sexual offending and
OL,12,Fpreference for extreme violent
OL,13,Fpornography dated back nearly 20 years
OL,14,Fbefore Ms Everard's murder.
OL,16,FMs Everard's family said in a
OL,17,Fstatement the abuse of his position
OL,18,Fled to her death.
