OL,7,F"We believe that Sarah died because he
OL,8,Fwas a police officer - she would never
OL,9,Fhave got into a stranger's car," her
OL,10,Fparents and siblings Sue, Jeremy,
OL,11,FKatie and James said.
OL,13,F"We strongly support the
OL,14,Frecommendations that Lady Elish has
OL,15,Fmade and trust that these will be
OL,16,Fimplemented forthwith. We cannot get
OL,17,FSarah back but positive changes give
OL,18,Fhope for the future and will be of
OL,19,Fbenefit to others.
