OL,7,F"It is almost three years now since
OL,8,FSarah died. We no longer wait for her
OL,9,Fcall; we no longer expect to see her.
OL,10,FWe know she won't be there at family
OL,11,Fgatherings. But the desperate longing
OL,12,Fto have her with us remains and the
OL,13,Flost of Sarah pervades every part of
OL,14,Four lives."
