OL,7,FMet Police Commissioner Sir Mark
OL,8,FRowley said in a press conference on
OL,9,FThursday: "One of the things that I
OL,10,Ftook from the report was how Wayne
OL,11,FCouzens was very careful to disguise
OL,12,Fand hide his corrupt and toxic and
OL,13,Fcriminal views and behaviours."
OL,15,FSir Mark said most officers who worked
OL,16,Fwith Couzens "had no inkling" and
OL,17,Fvowed to find staff exhibiting
OL,18,Fsimilar, concerning behaviour.
