OL,7,F"We're going to be relentless about
OL,8,Fthis, I need to reassure women and
OL,9,Fchildren in London that we really get
OL,10,Fthis," he added.
OL,12,FThe Home Office said the government
OL,13,Fsaid will "thoroughly consider the
OL,14,Frecommendations" made by the report .
