OL,7,F"Since 2021, the government has been
OL,8,Fdriving forward a body of work to
OL,9,Fstrengthen the way police officers are
OL,10,Fvetted, scrutinised and disciplined,
OL,11,Fand more broadly, efforts to put a
OL,12,Fstop to violence against women and
OL,13,Fgirls," the department said in its
OL,14,Fresponse.
OL,16,F"However, the report today highlights
OL,17,Fthe need for further action and the
OL,18,FGovernment, in tandem with policing
OL,19,Fpartners, will thoroughly consider the
OL,20,Frecommendations made by Lady Elish and
OL,21,Frespond in full in due course."
