OL,7,FAddressing MPs in the Commons, Home
OL,8,FSecretary James Cleverly announced
OL,9,Fpolice officers will be automatically
OL,10,Fsuspended in future if charged with
OL,11,Fcertain criminal offences.
OL,13,F"There will be a presumption for
OL,14,Fdismissal for any officer found to
OL,15,Fhave committed gross misconduct.
OL,17,F"I can announce today that there will
OL,18,Falso be an automatic suspension of
OL,19,Fpolice officers charged with certain
OL,20,Fcriminal offences."
